summary:
Experienced multilingual (Native Arabic, fluent English, fluent French and Dutch) Communication and Public Relations Officer. 
Solid background in web content writing and editing.
Sworn Legal translator in criminal law.
Excellent skills in  networking, public and media relations. 
Ability to organize big scale events, seminars, conferences and summits. 
Self-motivated, energetic, analytical and proactive person.
